{
  "stem": "4693.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once you finished at university, the Polish government restricted the possibility for Jews to join the profession by all closing, in some respects, admissions for Jews or by putting them to this type of exams where they couldn't pass.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was affected, because I was already a university graduate before the outbreak of the war in '35, '36.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also-- and I could not-- I knew that I would have difficulties.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was very pessimistic as far as a future of Jews in Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was very pessimistic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew-- I expected a war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have here a correspondence with my brother in Israel, who left in '34.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, in '36 or so, I was writing to him and telling him that it's-- that it's only a matter of years before the-- a few years before the war will come.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I expect German attack, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, not to this degree as they were singled out later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] they were killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I didn't expect that it would go so far.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I expected that definitely they will suffer greatly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It it's much easier to migrate when you see the writing on the suitcases, and has nothing behind you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You don't leave anything behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once you are established it's much harder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somewhere, the mental process is different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's much harder to make the decision to leave your parents, to leave your family, to leave everything and go.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was probably is the reason by all the migrations from Europe be to United States in the beginning of the 20th century, or end of the 19th.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who are migrating?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have any relatives or friends in the United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because only the very poor people migrated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The people had nothing to risk, nothing to give up.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
